              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssegmentedcell/1500200-trackingmode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of the segmented cell is set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssegmentswitchtracking/nssegmentswitchtrackingmomentary"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", then attempting to set the selected state of the segment will have no effect."
